<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('../images/logo.png') }}"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('../css/bootstrap.min.css') }}">
    <title>{% block title %}Hubert Furmański - Programowanie w Internecie{% endblock %}</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="main">
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ path('main') }}">Strona główna</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarColor01"
                        aria-controls="navbarColor01" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>

                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarColor01">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item active">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('projekt') }}">Projekt <span
                                        class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('o_mnie') }}">O mnie</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('kontakt') }}">Kontakt</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="https://github.com/Furm4n/PWI-Projekt-1">Repozytorium</a>
                        </li>
                        {% if app.user %}
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">Wyloguj się</a>
                            </li>
                            </a>
                        {% else %}
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_login') }}">Zaloguj się</a>
                            </li>
                        {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1 class="display-3">Witaj na mojej stronie!</h1>
            <p class="lead">Programowanie w internecie - projekt powstał przy użyciu frameworka Symfony PHP</p>
            <p class="lead"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://github.com/Furm4n/PWI-Projekt-1"
                               role="button">Repozytorium GitHub</a></p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="lead">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris ante ante, volutpat in diam et,
                convallis sodales nisi. Donec a suscipit lacus. Aliquam tellus ex, rhoncus ut dignissim vitae, aliquam
